headline: Marsh McLennan to Host First Quarter Earnings Investor Call on April 17
summary: NEW YORK, March 20, 2025--Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC), a global leader in risk, strategy and people, will announce first quarter financial results via news release on Thursday, April 17, 2025, before the market opens. The news release will be available on marshmclennan.com.
